<HEADLINE>
`STIGMATA' TOPS LIST; OH, THE HORROR!
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE McNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES -- The supernatural continued to hold sway at the
