4. ``Runaway Bride,'' $3.9 million. &QL; 
5. ``Bowfinger,'' $3.7 million. &QL; 
6. ``The 13th Warrior,'' $2.9 million. &QL; 
7. ``The Thomas Crown Affair,'' $2.8 million. &QL; 
8. ``Mickey Blue Eyes,'' $2.3 million. &QL; 
9. ``Chill Factor,'' $1.9 million. &QL; 
10. ``The Blair Witch Project,'' $1.6 million.
</P>
