<SLUG> BC-R-GUN-OWNERS-REVIEW-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE FACE OF GUNS: WHO OWNS THEM AND WHY 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (editors: this is the text that accompanies a photo essay)  
 996-0089)  
 (ART ADV: Photos are being sent to NYT photo clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.)  
 (bl)  
 By SAM HOWE VERHOVEK   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
