editor of the New York Times Week in Review, reflects gun owners
(all those pictured say their guns are legal) who offer a range of
other reasons for owning a weapon: for sport, for hunting, for
collecting, for self-protection (against rattlesnakes as well as
human intruders), for sentimental reasons and as a financial
investment.
</P>
