<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-13 13:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0239 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-SCI-MANSON-ART-BOS &LR;      09-13 1429
