 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Internet offers an enormous amout of information on the Y2K
bug.
</P>
<P>
   While some Web sites are operated by religious fanatics eager to
see society break down, or profiteers who hope to make money by
exploiting Y2K fears, dozens of sites are operated by responsible
organizations offering practical advice and factual updates.
</P>
<P>
   Here are just a few of the many good sites to visit.
