<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 UPDATE &HT;    UPDATE
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Tuesday, Sept. 14,
1999.
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
