<HEADLINE>
CONGRESS HAD EVIDENCE OF TEAR GAS CANISTERS IN 1995, DEMOCRAT SAYS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service Clients) 
By RON HUTCHESON 
And GABRIELLE CRIST 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
